lead_paragraph: Russian Sports Minister Vitaly Mutko said on Wednesday new doping allegations from German broadcaster ARD/WDR were aimed at influencing a ruling by the International Athletics Federation on Russia's suspension from world athletics, Interfax news agency reported.

headline.print_headline: Russian Sports Minister Says ARD Film Attempt to Sway IAAF: Ifax
